# Workspace scope

| Path | Stack | Rules |
|------|--------|--------|
| **backend/** | Java, Spring Boot | `java-*.mdc` (includes **java-naming**, **java-reuse-utils**), `db-migrations.mdc` |
| **backend/src/main/resources/migration/** | Flyway SQL | `db-migrations.mdc` |
| **frontend/** | React 18, TypeScript, Vite, Tailwind | `frontend-react-typescript.mdc`, **frontend-reuse-utils** |

When editing a file, follow the conventions for that path. Do not apply Spring/Java API patterns to React code or vice versa.
